All backend files from the design specification have been implemented. Here's a summary of what was created:

## Job Service Handlers

1. **`services/job-service/handlers/quota.go`** - Print quota management endpoints
   - Check quota availability
   - List/set/delete quotas
   - Quota history and summary
   - Repository: `quota_repository.go`

2. **`services/job-service/handlers/cost.go`** - Cost calculation endpoints
   - Cost configuration management
   - Calculate job costs
   - Cost reports by period/user/printer
   - Budget allocation tracking
   - Repository: `cost_repository.go`

3. **`services/job-service/handlers/secure_release.go`** - Secure print release endpoints
   - Hold jobs for secure release
   - Release with PIN/card/NFC
   - Release station management
   - Repository: `secure_release_repository.go`

4. **`services/job-service/handlers/reports.go`** - Advanced reporting endpoints
   - Usage summaries
   - Top users/printers
   - Department reports
   - Environmental impact reports
   - Trend data and exports
   - Repository: `reports_repository.go`

## Storage Service Handlers

5. **`services/storage-service/handlers/watermark.go`** - Document watermarking endpoints
   - Watermark template management
   - Apply watermarks to documents
   - Batch operations
   - Repository: `watermark_repository.go`

## Auth Service Handlers

6. **`services/auth-service/handlers/sessions.go`** - httpOnly cookie support
   - Login with cookies
   - Token refresh via cookies
   - Session management
   - Revoke sessions

## Middleware

7. **`internal/middleware/cookie_auth.go`** - Cookie authentication middleware
   - Authenticate from httpOnly cookies
   - Fallback to Authorization header
   - CORS with credentials support

## Registry Service Handlers

8. **`services/registry-service/handlers/mobile.go`** - Mobile app support endpoints
   - Device registration
   - Printer pairing via codes
   - Nearby printers discovery
   - Push notifications

## API Gateway

9. **`services/api-gateway/main.go`** - API Gateway service
   - Unified API entry point
   - Reverse proxy to all services
   - Request routing

10. **`services/api-gateway/handlers/developer.go`** - Developer portal endpoints
    - API key management
    - Usage statistics
    - Webhook management
    - API documentation

11. **`services/api-gateway/middleware/rate_limit.go`** - Rate limiting middleware
12. **`services/api-gateway/middleware/audit.go`** - Audit logging middleware

## Database Migrations

13. **`migrations/000027_create_watermark_templates.up.sql`** - Watermark templates and related tables
    - Watermark templates
    - Budget allocations
    - Scheduled reports
    - Mobile devices
    - Push notifications
    - API keys and usage logs
    - Webhooks and audit logs
14. **`migrations/000027_create_watermark_templates.down.sql`** - Rollback migration
